title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: When opening the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values are not displayed.
OB: When opening the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values are not displayed.
EB: When opening the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values should be displayed.
SR:
1. Open the application and navigate to the report page.
2. Click on the 'Show Report Parameters' button.
3. Verify that the default values for the parameters are not displayed.
